Bandwidth Products On EnronOnline Revised Forwarded by Leonardo PachecoCorpEnron on PM Leonardo Pacheco PM To Jay HawthornEnron nron Communications Tom CT Mark CT Rudi CT Jeff CT cc David nron Dale CT Cynthia HarknessEnron nron Communications Subject Bandwidth Products On EnronOnline Revised Please note that we have added another product type bringing the total number to three We have built three new Products Types called US Bandwidth DS Physical Forward US Bandwidth OC Physical Forward and US Bandwidth OCc Physical Forward Please go into DataManager and approve these Product Types look at attached Document for long descriptions We are going life on the st of May If you need help with the approval process contact Dale Neuner ext or myself ext Please Do Not Reject the Product Type If you have questions or changes to the Product Type please contact me at your convenience Thank you very much for your cooperation Leonardo Pacheco ext
